<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portal Terpadu Fakultas</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://unpkg.com/@basecoat/basecoat/dist/basecoat.min.css">
    <style>
        :root { --unand-green: #006837; --unand-yellow: #f9ed32; }
        body { background-color: #f8f9fa; color: #1a1a1a; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; }
        .navbar { background-color: var(--unand-green); color: white; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; border-bottom: 5px solid var(--unand-yellow); margin-bottom: 2rem; }
        .container { max-width: 1000px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 1rem; }
        .grid-menu { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 1.5rem; margin-top: 2rem; }
        .menu-card { background: white; padding: 2rem; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #ddd; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05); transition: transform 0.2s; }
        .menu-card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }
        .btn-unand { display: block; padding: 0.8rem; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 1rem; color: white !important; }
        .stat-badge { background: #e6f4ea; color: var(--unand-green); padding: 0.3rem 0.8rem; border-radius: 20px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        
        /* Cleaned up Login Box */
        .login-box { text-align: center; background: white; padding: 3rem; border-radius: 8px; border-top: 6px solid var(--unand-green); box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .role-btn { display: inline-block; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 12px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; color: white !important; transition: opacity 0.2s; }
        .role-btn:hover { opacity: 0.9; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav class="navbar">
        <div class="container" style="display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <div>
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 1.5rem;">Portal Terpadu Fakultas</h1>
                <p style="margin: 0; opacity: 0.9;">Sistem Pengajuan Pengunduran Diri Mahasiswa</p>
            </div>
            <% if (role) { %>
                <div style="text-align: right;">
                    <a href="/logout" style="color: white; text-decoration: underline; font-size: 0.9rem;">Keluar (Logout)</a>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        
        <% if (!role) { %>
            <div class="login-box">
                <h2 style="color: var(--unand-green); margin-top: 0;">Pilih Portal Layanan</h2>
                <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 2rem;">Silakan pilih portal sesuai dengan peran Anda untuk masuk ke dalam sistem.</p>
                
                <a href="/login" class="role-btn" style="background: #0056b3;">🎓 Portal Mahasiswa</a>
                <a href="/login" class="role-btn" style="background: #28a745;">👨‍🏫 Portal Ketua Program Studi</a>
                <a href="/login" class="role-btn" style="background: #d39e00;">🏛️ Portal Wakil Dekan 1</a>
                <a href="/login" class="role-btn" style="background: #333;">🔍 Portal Admin Akademik</a>
                
                <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #999; margin-top: 1.5rem;">Sistem dilengkapi otentikasi terpusat. Anda akan diarahkan ke halaman login yang aman.</p>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <% if (role) { %>
            <div style="background: white; padding: 2rem; border-left: 6px solid var(--unand-green); border-radius: 4px; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2 style="margin-top: 0; color: var(--unand-green);">Selamat Datang, <%= role.toUpperCase() %></h2>
                <p>Ini adalah area kerja khusus Anda. Anda hanya memiliki akses ke modul yang relevan dengan jabatan Anda.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="grid-menu">
                
                <% if (role === 'kaprodi') { %>
                <div class="menu-card" style="border-top: 4px solid #28a745;">
                    <h3 style="color: #28a745; margin-top:0;">Panel Kaprodi</h3>
                    <p>Fitur untuk meninjau dan memberikan persetujuan tingkat prodi.</p>
                    <div style="margin: 1rem 0;">Menunggu Verifikasi: <span class="stat-badge"><%= stats.kaprodi || 0 %></span></div>
                    <a href="/kaprodi" class="btn-unand" style="background: #28a745;">Buka Inbox Kaprodi</a>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <% if (role === 'wd1') { %>
                <div class="menu-card" style="border-top: 4px solid var(--unand-yellow);">
                    <h3 style="color: #856404; margin-top:0;">Panel Wakil Dekan 1</h3>
                    <p>Fitur pengesahan akhir Surat Keputusan (SK) Pengunduran Diri.</p>
                    <div style="margin: 1rem 0;">Menunggu Pengesahan: <span class="stat-badge" style="background:#fff3cd; color:#856404;"><%= stats.wd1 || 0 %></span></div>
                    <a href="/dekan" class="btn-unand" style="background: #d39e00;">Buka Inbox dekan</a>
                </div>
                <% } %>

                <% if (role === 'admin') { %>
                <div class="menu-card" style="border-top: 4px solid #333;">
                    <h3 style="color: #333; margin-top:0;">Radar Pelacakan</h3>
                    <p>Mesin pencari global terintegrasi untuk melacak status dokumen.</p>
                    <div style="margin: 1rem 0;">Total Berkas: <span class="stat-badge" style="background: #eee; color: #333;"><%= stats.total || 0 %></span></div>
                    <a href="/admin" class="btn-unand" style="background: #333;">Buka Radar Global</a>
                </div>
                <% } %>

            </div>
        <% } %>

    </div>
</body>
</html>